{"tid":1309181,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"吉野家刪除之前諷刺黑警「獅子狗」廣告 雲海","createTime":"2019-07-12T05:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T12:53:00.000Z","uid":49391,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81178bb2c140994605311899e220508ac28862b5","tid":1309181,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"吉野家刪除之前諷刺黑警「獅子狗」廣告，公司高層仲炒埋負責員工，同廣告代理結束合約，仲話吉野家高層參與過撐警活動，支持政府立場，仲話出現呢個廣告極度憤怒！<br />\n<br />\n嘩！好有立場啊！我真係好彩從來都唔食吉野家！你放心，佢哋親建制到咁，都一定大把人食！因為平大晒呀嘛而家！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/2858484824193633?__tn__=H-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCHANWANHOI%2Fposts%2F2858484824193633%3F__tn__%3DH-R&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUygu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=4ccdb479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/2858484824193633?__tn__=H-R</a><br />\nGood0Bad1[/url]"},{"pid":"c99340881ea6a06ace015b48bdaaad9191a1445f","tid":1309181,"uid":49391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gbzwnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gbzwnV.jpg&h=c2d28471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前香港吉野家在其 Facebook 專頁發帖，指「想食獅子狗，唔只大埔有。嘢可以亂食，名唔可以亂叫」，一張為「獅子狗」正名叫「竹輪」的抽水廣告，似是暗諷大埔「連儂隧道」有大批防暴警察，撕走相關紙張，被網民戲稱該批防暴警察是「撕紙狗」一事，因而獲得一眾網民「會心微笑」兼力讚，更表示揚言要多食吉野家以示支持。"},{"pid":"0d7579372d2e208ef5ea1c09562328dad6da865b","tid":1309181,"uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/145wyCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F145wyCT.jpg&h=c31bfc6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9d2cb40ba37b22779005bf43730bb5ca5281e39","tid":1309181,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d7579372d2e208ef5ea1c09562328dad6da865b","tid":1309181,"uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"repl